.git
.gitignore
node_modules
**/node_modules
packages/webui/dist
dist
.env
.env.*
!.env.template
.claude
.vscode
*.log
# Tests and colocated specs
tests
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts
# Docs / repo meta — not needed in the runtime image
CLAUDE.md
README.md
**/CLAUDE.md
**/README.md
deploy
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
.github
.forgejo
# The Claude Code hook is installed separately as a plugin — not part of the
# webapi/webui runtime image.
hook

# docs/ Markdown is a build input for the docs static-build stage (rendered to
# HTML by scripts/build-docs.ts). Re-include it despite the README.md excludes
# above; the runtime stage copies only the rendered output, not the raw Markdown.
!docs
!docs/**
